p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:3pt 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得注意的是，3月30日</span></span></span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">10:33官方在服务运行状态页面公告“故障已经修复”</span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，并继续监控其他可能的问题。此前，一位接近DeepSeek的知情人士强调，“今天肯定会修好。”</sp