-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据DeepSeek官方状态页公布的信息，DeepSeek于3月30日00:20首次介入问题排查，并在01:24和09:13两次发布修复更新并监控修复结果，到第二次发布修复更新，服务中断接近9个小时，到问题最终解决，整体持续10个小时左右。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:3pt 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从实测的情况来看，</span></span></span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第二次更新修复之后可以正常登录，但无法进入有效的对话</span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，输入提示词，AI助手会展示思维链，但无法正常“吐”答案，</span></span></span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">10:33这一轮修复后，AI助手的对话已经回复正常。</span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:3pt 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transpar